                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10133" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0304</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">290 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医工融合，向新而生：ESG“健康引擎”助力京东方高质量发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Medical-Industrial Integration, Born to be New: ESG&#39;s &quot;Health Engine&quot; Boosts BOE&#39;s High-Quality Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许晓芳，陶孜怡，吕思寒</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">京东方科技集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">京东方；智慧医工；ESG；公司治理；高质量发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> BOE; Intelligent Medical-Engineering; ESG; Corporate Governance; High-Quality Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球可持续发展与“健康中国”战略的双重驱动下，京东方作为全球显示技术领军企业，以“医工融合”为战略核心，开拓出智慧医工业务，将显示、物联网、人工智能等前沿技术与医疗健康场景深度融合，构建ESG“健康引擎”，驱动企业向高质量发展跃迁。环境保护方面，京东方通过践行绿色运营和加强环境管理，显著降低医疗场景的碳足迹；社会责任层面，京东方通过数字医疗全生命周期健康服务、员工福祉体系和社会公益活动等项目，展示其全面的责任担当；治理责任领域，主导制定国际标准，构建了透明高效的医疗管理体系，从而引领行业规范化发展。从企业高质量发展的视角来看，京东方全要素生产率呈现出持续攀升且显著领先行业均值的态势，表明了企业的“社会价值”和“经济效益”向高质量发展的升级转化。京东方的实践表明，ESG框架与“医工融合”战略的深度协同，展现了其在技术手段革新、管理流程优化、品牌形象树立、行业话语权提升方面的领先地位，赋能企业走向高质量发展之路。未来，京东方将继续深入贯彻“绿色+科技”理念，向新而生，实现企业稳健经营和高质永续发展，为人类美好生活贡献更多智慧与力量。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Under the dual drivers of global sustainable development and the &quot;Healthy China&quot; strategy, BOE, as a global leader in display technology, has established &quot;Medical-Engineering Integration&quot; as its strategic core to pioneer smart healthcare initiatives. By deeply integrating cutting-edge technologies such as display, IoT, and AI with healthcare scenarios, the company has constructed an ESG &quot;Health Engine&quot; to propel its transition toward high-quality development. In environmental protection, BOE significantly reduces carbon footprints in medical settings through green operations and enhanced environmental management. On social responsibility, the company demonstrates comprehensive commitment through digital healthcare services across full lifecycles, employee welfare systems, and social welfare programs. In governance, BOE leads industry standardization by establishing international standards and building transparent, efficient healthcare management systems. From the perspective of corporate high-quality development, BOE&#39;s total factor productivity (TFP) shows sustained growth significantly outperforming industry averages, reflecting successful upgrading of both &quot;social value&quot; and &quot;economic benefits&quot; to high-quality development. BOE&#39;s practices demonstrate that the deep synergy between its ESG framework and &quot;Medical-Engineering Integration&quot; strategy highlights leadership in technological innovation, management optimization, brand enhancement, and industry influence empowerment. Looking forward, BOE will continue implementing its &quot;Green + Technology&quot; idea, to live up to the new, to achieve stable operations and sustainable high-quality development, while contributing more technological wisdom and strength to enhance human well-being.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《企业社会责任》、《公司战略》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG理论；可持续发展理论；企业社会责任；高质量发展；竞争优势理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
